1. preuzeo xampp

2. preuzeo composer -> https://getcomposer.org/download/
prilikom instalacije odabrati -> php.exe iz vašeg XAMPP php direktorija (obično se nalazi unutar C:\xampp\php\php.exe
add this PHP to your path -> označiti

3. composer global require laravel/installer
-- prije ovoga uključiti zip u php ini --> extension=zip

4. u htdocs direktoriju
composer global require laravel/installer
laravel new example-app

5. instalacija node.js 
6. Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope LocalMachine -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned --> inače node.js ne radi u VSC terminalu
